\sum _{k=1}^{n-1} (n-k)\cos\frac{2k\pi}{n} 
n^{th}
n\sum_{k=1}^{n-1}\cos\frac{2k\pi}{n} -[ \sum_{k=1}^{n-1} cos\frac{2k\pi}{n}] -[\sum_{k=2}^{n-1} cos\frac{2k\pi}{n}]-[\sum_{k=3}^{n-1} cos\frac{2k\pi}{n}].........-[\sum_{k=(n-2)}^{n-1} cos\frac{2k\pi}{n}]-cos\frac{2\pi}{n}
\displaystyle\sum _{k=1}^{n-1} (n-k)\cos\frac{2k\pi}{n}= 
\displaystyle\sum _{k=1}^{n-1} (n-k)e^{\frac{2k\pi i}n}=
\displaystyle\sum _{k=1}^{n-1} (n-k)(e^{\frac{2\pi i}n})^k
\displaystyle\sum _{k=1}^{n-1} (n-k) x^k=n\sum _{k=1}^{n-1}x^k-\sum _{k=1}^{n-1} k x^k
\displaystyle\sum _{k=1}^{n-1} k x^k=x\frac{d(\sum _{k=0}^{n-1}x^k)}{dx}
